<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to [Your Car Platform Name]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 150px;
        }
        .hero {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <img src="https://your-logo-url.com/logo.png" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
    <h2>Welcome to [Your Car Platform Name]!</h2>
    
    <img src="https://your-car-image-url.com/car.jpg" alt="Luxury Car" class="hero">

    <p>Dear <strong>${name}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining <strong>[Your Car Platform Name]</strong>, the best place to buy and sell cars effortlessly. Start exploring now and find your dream car or list your vehicle in just a few clicks.</p>
    
    <a href="https://your-website.com" class="cta-button">Explore Now</a>

    <p class="footer">Need help? <a href="mailto:support@yourwebsite.com">Contact Support</a></p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
